## Component Overview

The features section highlights key selling points and benefits:

- **Free Shipping** — Threshold-based free delivery
- **Quality Guarantee** — Premium materials assurance
- **Fast Delivery** — Estimated shipping times
- **Expert Support** — Customer service information
- **Secure Payment** — Safe checkout guarantee

## Feature Types

### Standard Features Grid

Default 3-column feature grid:

```
``````liquid
&#123;% section 'features' %&#125;
```
**Features:**
- Free Shipping (€100+ orders)
- Quality Guaranteed
- Fast Delivery (2-5 days)

### Features with Background

Features with decorative background:

```liquid
```liquid
```
&#123;% section 'features-background', 
  background_color: '#0A0E16'
%&#125;
```
### Alternating Features

Features with alternating icon/text sides:

```
``````liquid
&#123;% section 'features-alternating', 
  features: [
    &#123; icon: 'truck', title: 'Free Shipping', text: 'On orders over €100' &#125;,
    &#123; icon: 'check', title: 'Quality Assured', text: 'Premium materials only' &#125;
  ]
%&#125;
```
## Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |
|-----------|------|---------|-------------|
| `features` | Array | Required | Array of feature objects |
| `layout` | Select | `grid` | Layout: `grid`, `alternating`, `list` |
| `background_color` | String | — | Background color for section |

## Usage Examples

### Standard Features Grid

```liquid
```liquid
```
&#123;% render 'section-features', 
  features: [
    &#123; icon: 'truck', title: 'Free Shipping', text: 'On all orders over €100' &#125;,
    &#123; icon: 'check', title: 'Quality Guaranteed', text: 'Premium materials, always' &#125;,
    &#123; icon: 'clock', title: 'Fast Delivery', text: '2-5 business days standard shipping' &#125;
  ]
%&#125;
```
### Features with Background

```
``````liquid
&#123;% render 'section-features', 
  features: [
    &#123; icon: 'truck', title: 'Free Shipping', text: '€100+ orders qualify' &#125;,
    &#123; icon: 'check', title: 'Quality Assured', text: 'Premium materials guaranteed' &#125;
  ],
  layout: 'grid',
  background_color: '#1A2033'
%&#125;
```
## CSS Classes

| Class | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `.features` | Features container |
| `.feature-block` | Individual feature block |
| `.feature-icon` | Feature icon element |
| `.feature-title` | Feature heading |
| `.feature-text` | Feature description |

## Accessibility

- All icons have aria-labels with descriptive text
- Focus visible on all interactive elements
- Screen readers announce feature titles correctly
- Keyboard navigation supported

